          h3 Constructing the grid
          p The precisoin used in the manufacturing the watch needed to be conveyed in its presentation. In 2011, Mark Boulton wrote A Richer Canvas, a treatise on web layout which confronted the incorrect model we had been using to construct grids on the web. It’s as important today as it was back then and I encourage you to read it if you work on the web. This was my first opportunity to put the ‘content out’  methodology into practice. 
          p 300 is nice, triangular number for us to use as a base unit deriving a sensible grid.

